五年過了從日本東北部大震災．我永遠不會忘記您們的幫助，我非常感謝臺灣和臺灣人．






國立臺灣大學海洋研究所　數理生態學研究室　三木　健
國立臺灣大學海洋研究所　數理生態學研究室　三木　健　
























2016.9 The paper on Fei-Tsui reservoir has been published. My contribution was to develop and numerically analyze the 1-dimensional methane-based food web model.

P-C Ho*, N Okuda, Takeshi Miki, M Itoh, F-K Shiah, C-W Chang, SSY Hsiao, S-J Kao, M Fujibayashi, C-H Hsieh (2016) Summer profundal hypoxia determines the coupling of methanotrophic production and the pelagic food web in a subtropical reservoir. Freshwater Biology 61: 1694-1706



 


 



